The paper presents a program repair technique that involves building a classifier and using a decision tree to synthesize a patch. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. Additionally, the paper deals with altering control flow to assist in program repair, which could also place it in the Programming Languages (cs.PL) sub-category. The use of a classifier and decision tree also suggests that the paper may be relevant to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with identifying and repairing defects, which could place it in the Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) sub-category.
